Package net.sourceforge.waters.analysis.comp552

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConflictAssessor
    The assessor for the COMP552 conflict checker programming assignments.
    ConflictChecker
    A dummy implementation of a conflict checker.
    ConflictCounterExampleChecker
    A tool to check whether a conflict counterexample is a correct counterexample to show that a given product DES is blocking.
    ConflictMain
    A sample main class for testing the ConflictChecker class.
    ControllabilityAssessor
    The assessor for explicit controllability checker programming assignments.
    ControllabilityChecker
    A dummy implementation of a controllability checker.
    ControllabilityCounterExampleChecker
    A tool to check whether a controllability counterexample is a correct counterexample to show that a given product DES is not controllable.
    ControllabilityMain
    A sample main class for testing the ControllabilityChecker class.
    ModelChecker
    An abstract class defining the interface of a model checker.
